GENERAL INSTRUCTIONS ON INSTALLATION:

0) Clone git repository:
	git clone https://github.com/johannesbakkelund/bismuth-antimony-tight-binding/

1) Install requirements:
	pip install numpy pandas scipy joblib matplotlib
	
2) Open download folder:
	cd bismuth-antimony-tight-binding
	
3) Install the package:
	pip install numpy pandas scipy joblib matplotlib
	
4) Create subfolders in the directory where you will run the package (parent folder):
	mkdir atom_types eigenvalues hopping_matrix k_points xsf edge_participation
	
5) Copy the folder "atom_positions" to the same directory, it contains atom position information
